description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 78, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 234, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 1 for East, 2 for South, and 3 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80783-51234-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [234 Votes, Top 5% Score]
